Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,In 1926, Robert Goddard launched and then crashed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,1926年  罗伯特·戈达德设计的火箭在发射后炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,the world's first liquid propellant rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是世界上第一个液体推进剂火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:09.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Its weird design falling afoul of the pendulum rocket fallacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:09.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,其怪异的设计落入了“钟摆式火箭”的谬误
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Intuitively, it makes sense to put your engines up top.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,从直觉上讲  把引擎放在顶部是很合理的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,If i hold this rocket from its bottom, then it just falls over;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果我在底部托着火箭  它很难立得稳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,but pulling from the top like a pendulum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是在顶部像钟摆一样挂着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,this one is able to stay stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个就能保持稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:22.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Likewise, during flght, we'd expect that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:22.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,在飞行时  我们自然也期望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:25.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,this heavy fuel section keeps the rocket pointing upward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:25.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,能靠沉重的油箱作为摆锤  来保持火箭朝上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:26.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,This doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:26.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,然并卵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm about to drop this 5 kilogram medicine ball and half kilo volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,我要丢下这个10斤的健身球和1斤的排球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:34.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,although the medicine ball is experiencing greater weight force
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:34.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,尽管健身球所受的重力大得多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,it also takes more force to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,但它的惯性也更大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:39.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,These factors cancel out and both balls land at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:39.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,这两个因素相互抵消  导致两个球会同时落地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:42.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Since the sections experience the same gravitational acceleration,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:42.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,由于上下两部分的重力加速度相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,weight alone can't write our structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,因而没法单靠重力来改变其结构
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,This isn't true in a pendulum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,而钟摆之所以能改变形态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,since the pivot is pinned in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,是因为上面的转轴已经钉死位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,The only way to change orientation is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,火箭想改变方向只有一种方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,with a sideways force providing rotational torque,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,就是给火箭一个侧向力  提供旋转扭矩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:55.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,but since the engines are fixed in position,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:55.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,但把引擎固定挂在上面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,no torque can be generated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,就无法产生扭矩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:59.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,喜欢这类火箭的人  给火箭加上尾翼吧
